      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is way way bigger than all the other xxxxxData types... it feels weird to me to jam it all in the middle of the IRNode class. Just to keep this code focused, is there somewhere else that TypeData can live, instead of the middle of IRNode.h?\n\nWe could put it in Type.h, or into a dedicated TypeData.h header...?",
